title: Enemy Line Part 1
description: While Optimus struggles to be a leader in peace-time, Bumblebee undertakes a daring mission into Decepticon territory.

title: The End of the Universe I Part 1
description: Starscream's fate at the hands of the Quintessons is revealed as he returns a three-headed Judge!

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: The Loop Part 1
description: It's a beautiful day on Cybertron and only Hot Rod doesn't seem to be enjoying the festive Parade of Metals.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 1
description: As the Autobots on the Ark prepare to land on Cybertron, Chromia and Perceptor attempt to escape Decepticon captivity.

title: The Scientist Part 2
description: While Hot Rod and Soundwave battle the indestructible Scientist, Perceptor and the rest of the team attempt a mass breakout from the Loop.

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: The Dead End Part 2
description: Hot Rod and Clobber attempt to convince a disoriented and distrustful Dead End to join them in their fight against the Quintessons.

title: The Judge Part 1
description: The Quintesson Judge and his forces assault Iaconus while Optimus and Megatron lead a strike team into the Quintesson ship.

title: Rack N' Ruin N' Ratchet Part 1
description: Rack'N'Ruin join Ratchet on a rescue mission to save Jetfire, who has gone down behind enemy lines.

title: The End of the Universe II Part 1
description: Windblade battles the Sharkticons to regain entry into Iaconus.

title: The Judge Part 2
description: Megatron and Optimus's strike team faces off against the Scientist while the Autobot and Decepticon defenders of Iaconus desperately keep the all-powerful Judge distracted.

title: The End of the Universe I Part 2
description: Judge Starscream interrogates his Cybetronian prisoners while Optimus, Bee, and Wheeljack try to get back through the Multiverse Bridge.

title: Battle for Cybertron IV Part 2
description: With Vector Sigma destroyed, Megatron and Shockwave make a desperate attempt to destroy the Allspark.

title: Dweller in the Depths Part 2
description: Optimus receives a dire warning from the Primes as Chromia and Bee pursue Windblade into a waking Titan under the sea.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: Journey to the Valley of Repugnus Part 2
description: Bee and Grimlock navigate the strange cultures of the Energon Masters and Monsterbots, uncovering a shocking secret about the two seemingly-different peoples.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 2
description: The Autobots distract the Decepticons with an all-out assault on the Threshold of the Well while Bee, Hot Rod, and Cheetor split off for the real mission…

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: The End of the Universe IV Part 2
description: Megatron returns from the Multiverse with enough new found powers to contest Judge Starscream, Windblade uses all her power attempting to free Croaton from Quintesson control.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 1
description: Megatron's jubilation at destroying the Ark is short-lived as he realizes the ship was a decoy — the Autobots have landed on Cybertron.

title: The Loop Part 2
description: After escaping The Loop, Hot Rod, Clobber and Perceptor must stay one step ahead of their terrifying pursuers.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 2
description: Chromia and Perceptor race to warn the Autobots that the Decepticons are waiting for them on Cybertron.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: The End of the Universe III Part 1
description: Windblade wakes the War Titan Iaconus, only to discover the Quintessons have a Titan of their own!

title: Enemy Line Part 2
description: Bee recovers a comatose Windblade from Shadowstriker and must shepherd her safely from Decepticon territory.

title: The End of the Universe IV Part 1
description: With Iaconus down, the Cybertronians make a desperate last stand against Judge Starscream.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 1
description: While the battle rages on the surface, deep below ground Hot Rod faces off against an unexpected traitor, giving Cheetor and Bee time to get the Allspark to the Well.

title: Alien Hunt! With Meteorfire and Cosmos Part 2
description: Bumblebee runs the gauntlet of creepily haunted Luna-3, while Meteorfire records everything on camera for his show.

title: Alien Hunt! With Meteorfire and Cosmos Part 1
description: Bumblebee enlists washed-up TV show host Meteorfire to help him find another of Windblade's psychic shards on Luna-3.

title: The Prisoner Part 2
description: The dysfunctional team capture a Sharkticon bailiff and Soundwave's attempts to sabotage Hot Rod's leadership don't go as planned.

title: Silent Strike Part 2
description: Megatron tries desperately to prevent The Other One from entering their universe.

title: The Prisoner Part 1
description: Hot Rod and Soundwave compete over leadership of the group, arguing over how to best defeat the Quintessons.

title: The Alliance Part 1
description: Freed from the Loop, Optimus and Megatron still have trouble reconciling so it's up to Hot Rod and Soundwave to unite the divided Cybertronians against the Quintesson invaders.

title: Rack N' Ruin N' Ratchet Part 2
description: Rack'N'Ruin must rescue the rescue mission when Astrotrain and Dead End kidnap Jetfire and Ratchet.

title: Silent Strike Part 1
description: Optimus and the Autobots infiltrate Decepticon Territory to destroy the Dark Matrix Megatron stole from a mysterious bot known only as "The Other One."

title: The End of the Universe II Part 2
description: While the Autobots and Decepticons stall Judge Starscream, Windblade tries to awaken Iaconus.

title: Dweller in the Depths Part 1
description: When a mysterious shark-bot named Hammerbyte kidnaps comatose Windblade, Bee and Chromia must chase him into the depths of the Argon Sea to retrieve her.

title: The Other One Part 2
description: The Other One reveals himself as an all-powerful Megatron from a universe where Optimus Prime is no more.

title: The End of the Universe III Part 2
description: Iaconus and Croaton do battle as Optimus, Bumblebee and Wheeljack contend with the Scientist.

title: The Scientist Part 1
description: In order to heal Soundwave's glitch and find out how to free the Autobots and Decepticons from the Loop, the team hunt down a mysterious Quintesson called The Scientist.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 2
description: Windblade, Wheeljack, and Teletraan-X make a play for Vector Sigma.

title: The Other One Part 1
description: The Other One and his Super Soldiers arrive, forcing Optimus and Megatron to fight together.

title: The Alliance Part 2
description: Autobots and Decepticons unite, launching a massive assault on the Quintesson ship.

title: Battle for Cybertron IV Part 1
description: Bee and Cheetor find new allies in the depths of Cybertron, Windblade, Wheeljack and Teletraan-X battle Bludgeon for control of Vector Sigma, and the Decepticons reveal their superior weaponry on the battlefield.

title: Journey to the Valley of Repugnus Part 1
description: Bumblebee and Grimlock are separated as they search the depths of Cybertron for another of Windblade's psychic shards, encountering the Monsterbots and the Energon Masters.

title: The Dead End Part 1
description: When Clobber enters the Deception Loop to rescue Lockdown, she attracts the attention of a different Decepticon instead.
